Nhaka Foundation last week officially unveiled newly renovated Early Childhood Centres (ECD) at five schools in Goromonzi District. The Foundation, in partnership with the Primary and Secondary Education ministry and the Goromonzi local community, renovated the ECD centres and helped construct play centres at the schools as part of their efforts to improve early childhood education in the country.The renovated ECD centres are at Munyawiri, Nyamande, Pote, Mutanhaurwa, Kachuta and Munyawiri Primary Schools in Domboshawa. &#8211; Tapiwa Zivira